          <title>To use a range of techniques to perform calculations [LO 1.8.2]</title>
          <para id="id20122431"/>
          <para id="id15462373">1. CHALLENGE!</para>
          <para id="id20979540">Choose any five items / articles that you are able to buy in a shop (they do not necessarily have to be groceries).</para>
