          <para id="id5877024">2. ANOTHER CHALLENGE!</para>
          <para id="id4462337">Arrange a class discussion and find answers to the following:</para>
          <para id="id4309714">2.1 What is a budget?</para>
          <para id="id21527785">2.2 Must families have a budget?</para>
          <para id="id8696700">2.3 Do YOU have a budget according to which you spend</para>
          <para id="id17499415"> your pocket money? If so, tell the class about it.</para>
